The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques such as style transfer, segmentation, and anti-aliasing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions augmented reality applications, which falls under cs.GR (Graphics). The use of Markov random field model suggests the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper involves machine learning techniques such as instance aware semantic segmentation, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves smoothing and anti-aliasing techniques, which may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
